Project 1: German Bakery Static Website
Live Demo: https://my-staticweb-demo1.s3.eu-central-1.amazonaws.com/index.html
Tech Stack: 
HTML5 + CSS3
AWS S3 (Static Website Hosting)

Deployment Steps:

1. Created a single responsive index.html file with inline CSS.
2. Created an S3 bucket and disabled "Block all public access".
3. Enabled Static Website Hosting (set index document to index.html).
4. Generated and applied a public read bucket policy using AWS Policy Generator:
{
  "Version": "2012-10-17",
  "Statement": [
    {
      "Sid": "Statement1",
      "Effect": "Allow",
      "Principal": "*",
      "Action": [
        "s3:GetObject"
      ],
      "Resource": "arn:aws:s3:::my-staticweb-demo1/*"
    }
  ]
}

5. Uploaded index.html to the bucket.
6. Tested the site via the S3 website endpoint on desktop and mobile.
